    }

    }

        string id PK
        string full_name
        string name
        string path
    }

        string id PK
        string full_name
        string name

    VENDOR {
        string id PK
        string name
    }

    VERSION }|--|{ COMMIT : PUSHES

    VENDOR ||--o{ COMPONENT : PUBLISHES

    USES {
        string times
        string version
        string type
    }

    CHANGED_TO {
        string diff
        int delta
    }

    "WORKFLOW COMMIT" }o--|| USES : ""
